OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784832502
OL,3,CCalls for the Welsh Government to
OL,4,Cfollow England with cap on bus fares
OL,6,FThere are calls for the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment to introduce a cap on bus
OL,8,Ffares after Andy Burnham announced a
OL,9,Fnew limit for England.
OL,11,FThe new Prime Minister, on his second
OL,12,Ffull day in office, announced most bus
OL,13,Ffares in England will be lowered from
OL,14,F#3 to #2 for a single journey from
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,17,FReform UK and Welsh Labour have have
OL,18,Fcalled on the Welsh Government to
OL,19,Ffollow suit and introduce a cap.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
