OL,3,CCalls for the Welsh Government to
OL,4,Cfollow England with cap on bus fares
OL,6,FKen Skates MS, Welsh Labour Leader
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's great to see the new Prime
OL,8,FMinister Andy Burnham acting quickly
OL,9,Fto give families some breathing space
OL,10,Fwith the cost of living.
OL,12,F"Introducing a #2 bus fare cap in
OL,13,FWales is of course a decision for the
OL,14,FWelsh Government. That's why Welsh
OL,15,FLabour had a manifesto commitment to
OL,16,Fdo just that.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
