PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784832502
OL,3,CCalls for the Welsh Government to
OL,4,Cfollow England with cap on bus fares
OL,6,F"This Plaid Cymru Government should
OL,7,Furgently look to introduce a cap in
OL,8,FWales. Otherwise people in Wales will
OL,9,Fbe left paying more for bus travel
OL,10,Fthan our neighbours across the border."
OL,12,FWhat is the situation in Wales?
OL,14,FIn Wales there is no universal cap on
OL,15,Fbus fares. However, 5-21 year olds
OL,16,Fsingle journeys are capped at #1.
OL,18,FOver 60s and disabled people can
OL,19,Ftravel for free on buses if they are a
OL,20,Fresident of Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
