PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784832502
OL,3,CCalls for the Welsh Government to
OL,4,Cfollow England with cap on bus fares
OL,6,FAs transport is a devolved issue it is
OL,7,Fup to the Welsh Government to decide
OL,8,Fwhether to introduce a cap or not.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government has indicated
OL,11,Fthey will not follow England in
OL,12,Fintroducing a cap on bus fares.
OL,14,FIn a statement the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fsaid: "Wales is leading the way on
OL,16,Faffordable, accessible public
OL,17,Ftransport.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
