PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784832502
OL,3,CCalls for the Welsh Government to
OL,4,Cfollow England with cap on bus fares
OL,6,F"We have already introduced #1 bus
OL,7,Ffares for young people aged 5 to 21 on
OL,8,Fservices across Wales, and our free
OL,9,Fbus pass scheme means over-60s and
OL,10,Fdisabled people can travel without
OL,11,Fpaying a penny.
OL,13,F"We have also confirmed plans for a
OL,14,Fnew coach service linking the north
OL,15,Fand south of Wales, improving
OL,16,Fconnectivity across the nation and
OL,17,Fcutting journey times by over an hour."
